{"title":"Pruebas de coagulación","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Pruebas de coagulación-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Pruebas de\\Ncoagulación","guid":"NplyQYFHhiG6h4QzUzMXaQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"1. Tests\\Ncomunes","guid":"1xdvxNibocUhML7hGuRTMQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Tiempo de\\Nprotrombina (PT):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• RR: 11-15 seg.","guid":"nS9PoIIjo6dbJMZalMPjPg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Descripción: Tiempo para formar polímeros de fibrina tras añadir tromboplastina y Ca.","guid":"nlyxX3omykr5jCOoW-Wzwg","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"• Vías: Extrínseca (✓) + Común (✓).","guid":"3DHYWMq8Mp-kCBhqj2MP-w","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"• Relevancia clínica:\\NAumenta en:","guid":"vYz1NDjOXa2WcnySm9dIkw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Déficit de vit. K","guid":"AFiX83NDRNX99hgYDd8pvQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Cirrosis (↓ prod. factores coagulación)","guid":"CD4GeBDuJSWXsNKU-lM3FA","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"• Deficiencia del factor VII","guid":"8a0BHKK1yctZ-MRP-x1afA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"6","text":"• CID","guid":"v2n3TfVUsj28V2XiWJ_KXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"2","text":"• Monitorización: Terapia con antagonistas de vit. K (INR).","guid":"FuE-Ted_XQ7MvOfEfFVKnw","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"• Índice Normalizado\\NInternacional (INR):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• RR: 0.9-1.1","guid":"mxiWbNxEus5rbM4vJ35Saw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Descripción: Derivado del PT, comparando PT de lab. específico con un PT estandarizado.","guid":"g6tFllPJM58w7d0Atnc4Eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"• Tiempo de tromboplastina\\Nparcial activado (aPTT/PTT):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• RR: 25-40 seg.","guid":"03S6tUoW7-wJDe5ne-7GMg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"• Descripción: Tiempo para formar polímeros de fibrina tras añadir fosfolípidos.","guid":"ZaQcLOE6rshNectGl31_LQ","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"• Vías: Intrínseca (✓) + Común (✓).","guid":"G-3J2toA-qnE2f1ku4pZiQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"• Relevancia clínica:\\NProlongado en:","guid":"24wjIz4IwVXGM3r-fplOPA","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Hemofilia","guid":"F_fE5Lq30ax0yXBjXgTDcA","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Déficit de vit. K","guid":"zFgxtpoXNl85wa7g7lZs0Q","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"• CID","guid":"AN8nDTuZVveCrubZWVE8xQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"19","text":"• Posible enf. de von Willebrand","guid":"eZ6M7D-d46DXZZZ_gdy4QQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"19","text":"• LES (anticoagulante lúpico presente)","guid":"86JlNBUFYzrlVRKnNYV9YQ","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"19","text":"• Monitorización: Terapia con heparina no fraccionada (UFH).","guid":"QArLwLZkcD9WIDRq7UjAWQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"1","text":"• Tiempo de\\Ntrombina (TT):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• RR: <2 seg. desviación del control.","guid":"ZP7oJDPG7GYrnlRCOjgDsw","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Descripción: Tiempo para formar polímeros de fibrina tras añadir trombina.","guid":"0D013zJDZatnsFJvXW-b8Q","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Vías: Común (✓).","guid":"L3nL79PdUV4fJ_H7ids_Yg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"• Relevancia\\Nclínica:","guid":"hETeTTXTsQ6SKsp9OdjXDg","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Evaluación de déficit de fibrinógeno.","guid":"ip6Ota-QYc18WT8keoS1yA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Monitorización: terapia con heparina y fibrinolíticos.","guid":"Yq5BWu24YbzORWvZNQzoJg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"1","text":"• Tiempo de\\Nreptilase:","guid":"aftOPl0PKFi_jkDn75S53Q","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• RR: 14-24 seg.","guid":"N26yEZMVuaSpjnWyIIGjsg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• Descripción: Tiempo para formar polímeros de fibrina tras añadir reptilase.","guid":"h_fjtsZj_scdaSmMEMTQnw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"• Vías: Común (✓).","guid":"3M4odxeMlHqs1KSpw7NfCQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"• Relevancia clínica: Evaluación de déficit de fibrinógeno.","guid":"lFRw3oAYWjZAscL8DL37PQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"0","text":"2. Tests adicionales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Tiempo de\\Nsangrado:","guid":"vRcyc9v6eE0VfphtX1-byw","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Descripción: Tiempo para detener un sangrado tras punción cutánea.","guid":"9eXrhJ_fYfxo7u1icPaD2w","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"• Prolongado en: Trastornos de hemostasia primaria (trombocitopenia, disfunción plaquetaria).","guid":"5bHq9vt6RRIVEGsnK4bvaQ","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"• Nota: No realizado rutinariamente.","guid":"xjePUHTD3ircWa6jBBn62g","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"38","text":"• Ensayo\\Nanti-factor Xa:","guid":"48S6CvQtrcLFEigkOlYN5g","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Usos:","guid":"xCrPb5T-6XW1C9wKn8glmA","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Monitorización de LMWH o fondaparinux en ptes con función renal ↓.","guid":"uxbAfo52P_ClcJGQlSjlpQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"• Terapia con UFH si aPTT es inconcluso (ej., deficiencia de\\Nfactores de coagulación, anticuerpos contra heparina).","guid":"A9pC6jpeVEI4KfP8XMMHQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"38","text":"• D-dímero:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Descripción: Producto de degradación de fibrina,\\Ncorrelaciona con actividad de coagulación y fibrinólisis.","guid":"JegnvtiOSIKVr7F5CxAXHg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Sensibilidad alta: ↑ en TEP, TVP, CID.","guid":"5e_0jmSFC107r6SfwjBLkw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"• Especificidad baja: ↑ en malignidad, infección,\\Nembarazo, insuficiencia renal, post-cirugía.","guid":"MrE-k3qQj-kw2laFvD1LYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"38","text":"• Ensayo de cofactor\\Nde ristocetina:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Descripción: Mide capacidad del vWF para aglutinar plaquetas.","guid":"TWON5y3TUXTnnvD2RAv_og","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"• Ristocetina: Ab que activa vWF, el cual se une a GpIb en plaquetas.","guid":"6nY8UMabLJ2Dp4NkrfO6nA","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"• Interpretación:","guid":"zBY2qV8x1897sl24ABIlhg","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• En enf. von Willebrand (↓ vWF) o sd. de Bernard-Soulier (↓ receptor de vWF en plaquetas), agregación\\Nplaquetaria ↓ o nivel de cofactor de ristocetina <30 IU/dL que se corrige con plasma normal.","guid":"RE-Hl0eiHUjJN6mrX6BLFA","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"• En trombastenia de Glanzmann, agregación plaquetaria normal en respuesta a ristocetina\\Npero falla en respuesta a otros agonistas (ADP, epinefrina, colágeno, trombina).","guid":"1FO4tMoqKiB8Ri-RrjVZ3w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Assays y tests de\\Ncoagulación:","guid":"LclmxxRZR8Sz8fbSh47FoQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"1. Coagulation\\Nfactor assays:","guid":"Gd0YX0ynLEC39-Pg75sjpw","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Ejemplo: ↓ actividad del\\Nfactor VIII en hemofilia A.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"2. Clot observation\\Ntest:","guid":"mTTYGmoHzLV-kVg5FLlGPQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Descripción: Método simple de evaluación en el punto\\Nde atención para valorar la coagulación, especialmente\\Nsi se sospecha hiperfibrinólisis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Procedimiento: Se recolecta una pequeña cantidad de\\Nsangre en un tubo de ensayo y se examina\\Nmacroscópicamente después de unos minutos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Interpretación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"• Formación de trombo estable:\\NCoagulación normal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"• Sin formación de trombos:\\NCoagulación gravemente\\Ndeteriorada (ej., en CID).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"60","text":"• Formación de trombo\\Ninestable que se disuelve\\Nrápidamente: Hiperfibrinólisis.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"57","text":"3. Trombografía:","guid":"dAnrO1YHPXzMUl274fl9Qw","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Descripción: Ensayo de sangre completa que\\Nevalúa la formación, estabilidad y disolución de un\\Ntrombo, junto con PT y aPTT.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"57","text":"4. Test de\\NRumpel-Leede:","guid":"ufzGiSrn1H6dGcb2SPtqHQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Descripción: Detecta trastornos\\Nde hemostasia primaria y ↑\\Nfragilidad capilar dérmica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Procedimiento: Se aplica un torniquete en el brazo\\Nsuperior y se infla el manguito a una presión intermedia\\Nentre la PAS y PAD del paciente. Tras 5 min, se retira el\\Ntorniquete y se examinan la fosa cubital y el antebrazo en\\Nbusca de petequias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"• Interpretación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"• Positivo: ≥10 petequias por\\Npulgada cuadrada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"69","text":"• Positivo en:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"69","text":"• Fiebre\\Nhemorrágica del\\Ndengue.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"69","text":"• Trastornos que afectan la hemostasia\\Nprimaria (ej., trombocitopenia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"69","text":"• ↑ fragilidad capilar (ej., uso prolongado\\Nde esteroides, escorbuto).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"69","text":"• Diátesis hemorrágica vascular\\N(ej., enf. de\\NOsler-Weber-Rendu, vasculitis\\NIgA).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"69","text":"• Escarlatina.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":79,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"Pruebas de coagulación-2024","id":"map_1088","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Pruebas de coagulación-2024"}